---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const principles = [
  { title: 'Operate in ambiguity.', body: "Most briefs are a Slack message. I'll write the API, sketch the doc, and ship a flag-gated version before asking for a clarification meeting." },
  { title: 'Bias for shipping over specification.', body: "Cheapest version that produces a fact, not the cheapest version that ships. These are different." },
  { title: 'Default to writing it down.', body: "200-word docs in #eng beat 4 sync meetings. Working notes earn their keep — half my best ideas came from re-reading a doc nobody else opened." },
  { title: 'Boring stack, sharp edges.', body: "Postgres, queues, idempotency. I'd rather pay for hosting than for novelty. The interesting work lives in the seams, not the substrate." },
];
---

<Base title="About — Akash Joshi" description="Who I am, how I work, and what I'm looking for.">
  <header class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-neutral-100">About</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-neutral-400">
      The longer, less-LinkedIn version.
    </p>
  </header>

  <section class="mb-14 space-y-4 max-w-prose text-neutral-300">
    <p>
      I&rsquo;m a founding engineer based in Mumbai. Currently at
      <a href="https://equal.in" class="text-neutral-100 underline decoration-neutral-700 hover:decoration-neutral-100 transition">Equal Identity</a>
      (Prosus-backed, ~$80M raised), working on India&rsquo;s RBI-regulated Account
      Aggregator framework — the consent and data-sharing rails that sit underneath every
      modern Indian fintech. I own a wider surface than the title implies: infrastructure,
      observability, internal tooling, and lately an agent-evaluation platform for an AI
      call-assistant product.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before this I was a founding engineer at two other fintechs — Yelow Autofin
      (lending, INR 20M disbursed in the first ten days) and SayF / Wealides Fintech
      (cashback + digital gold, 120K users, INR 1B+ TPV, Titan-Capital backed). The
      headline number — <em>0 → 1M transactions</em> — is real; the
      <a href="/writing/zero-to-one-million-transactions" class="text-neutral-100 underline decoration-neutral-700 hover:decoration-neutral-100 transition">long version with the regrets</a>
      is on the writing side of this site.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before that I studied Computer Engineering at the University of Mumbai (Bharati
      Vidyapeeth CoE), graduated in 2024 with a 9.1/10 CGPA, and won a couple of
      hackathons along the way — including Smart India Hackathon 2022 on a DRDO problem
      statement, felicitated by the Vice President of India.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-14" aria-labelledby="how-i-work">
    <h2 id="how-i-work" class="mb-6 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-500">
      How I work
    </h2>
    <ol class="space-y-5">
      {principles.map((p, i) => (
        <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-4">
          <span class="text-xs tabular-nums text-neutral-600 pt-1">0{i + 1}</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-[15.5px] font-medium text-neutral-100">{p.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-400">{p.body}</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-14" aria-labelledby="reach">
    <h2 id="reach" class="mb-6 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-500">
      How to reach me
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-prose text-neutral-400">
      Open to remote roles, fintech-infra and AI-in-product collaborations, and the
      occasional &ldquo;can I pick your brain about AA&rdquo; conversation (yes, you can).
    </p>
    <dl class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-[6rem_1fr] gap-y-2 text-sm">
      <dt class="text-neutral-600 uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-xs pt-[3px]">Email</dt>
      <dd>
        <a href="mailto:theskyspacedev@gmail.com" class="text-neutral-100 underline decoration-neutral-700 hover:decoration-neutral-100 transition select-all">theskyspacedev@gmail.com</a>
      </dd>
      <dt class="text-neutral-600 uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-xs pt-[3px]">LinkedIn</dt>
      <dd>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/theskyspace" class="text-neutral-100 underline decoration-neutral-700 hover:decoration-neutral-100 transition">linkedin.com/in/theskyspace</a>
        <span class="text-neutral-600"> · fastest</span>
      </dd>
      <dt class="text-neutral-600 uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-xs pt-[3px]">GitHub</dt>
      <dd>
        <a href="https://github.com/theskyspace" class="text-neutral-100 underline decoration-neutral-700 hover:decoration-neutral-100 transition">github.com/theskyspace</a>
      </dd>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="colophon">
    <h2 id="colophon" class="mb-6 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-500">
      About this site
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-prose text-sm text-neutral-500">
      Built with <a href="https://astro.build" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-100 underline decoration-neutral-800 hover:decoration-neutral-100 transition">Astro</a>,
      Tailwind v4, and MDX. Content lives in plain Markdown so I can edit it in Obsidian.
      Source on <a href="https://github.com/theskyspace" class="text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-100 underline decoration-neutral-800 hover:decoration-neutral-100 transition">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
